  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Portfolio Manager (Real Estate)",
  "description": "<p>A private investment firm with an established European real estate platform is seeking a <strong>Portfolio Manager</strong> to oversee and drive value across its UK and EU real estate portfolios.</p><p>This role sits at the intersection of <strong>asset management, portfolio strategy, and execution</strong>, with direct accountability for performance, valuation uplift, and divestment outcomes.</p><p>Candidates who may not have covered UK/EU markets but have strong experience in Real Estate Portfolio Management are also encouraged to apply.</p><p><strong>Why This Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Direct ownership of portfolio strategy and outcomes</li><li>Exposure to large-scale, institutional-quality European real estate assets</li><li>Stable capital base with long-term investment horizon</li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and oversee multiple real estate portfolios across the UK and EU with significant AUM</li><li>Lead asset management strategy to drive portfolio performance, valuation uplift and return optimisation</li><li>Work closely with operating partners, brokers, legal and financial advisors on asset-level initiatives</li><li>Develop and execute divestment strategies, including sale processes and transaction execution</li><li>Provide portfolio-level analysis, valuation insights and strategic recommendations to senior stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>Ideal Background</strong></p><ul><li>7–12+ years of experience in real estate portfolio management, asset management, or principal investing</li><li>Proven track record managing European real estate assets, particularly in the UK and EU</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please click \"Apply Now\".</p><p>Company Reg No.: 201131609D | License No.: 24S2411 | Reg No: R22109164 | Valenzuela Alexandra Marie Tolentino</p>",
